  "response": "Ramsay Bolton's actions towards Sansa Stark on their wedding night are rooted in his cruel and sadistic nature. Ramsay is known for his brutality and enjoys exerting power and control over others, often through psychological and physical torment. By mistreating Sansa, he aims to assert his dominance and instill fear, reinforcing his authority and breaking her spirit. This behavior is consistent with his character throughout the series, where he takes pleasure in the suffering of others and uses it as a means to maintain control and manipulate those around him.",
